        public void insertNode(int newBNumber,
                       java.lang.String newCourse)
        insertNode public method. To create and clone respective Nodes and to insert the same in BST structure. BST - Binary Search Tree. 1st creates the original node. 2nd creates 2 clones for backup1 and backup2. 3rd Inserts the original and cloned nodes to the BST structure using private InsertNode method. 4th addes the cloned backup nodes to the node array list for reference in original node.
